    <arm_group_label>rotational technique</arm_group_label>
    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>After insertion of the entire cuff inside the mouth, the LMA FlexibleTM was rotated counter-clockwise through 90° and was advanced through the right side of the tongue until the resistance was felt, and then was returned back in the hypopharynx.</description>
